data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful 3 bedrooms, 2 bath home located in a well established Shenandoah neighborhood. It features a family room, formal living and large dining area which connects to the spacious kitchen. Master Suite has a full bath and beautiful custom vanity. Close to shopping, restaurants, grocery stores and mall area. Home has been freshly painted, screened in back porch area that leads out to the oversize deck and huge backyard for entertaining family and friends. Easy access to main roads, I-295, Ft Liberty, former Fort Bragg, and Mall area. Schedule your showing today.
